Here are a few of my favorites:

The Tiger Rising, by Kate DiCamillo
Becoming Naomi Leon, by Pam Munoz Ryan
The Alice Series, by Phyllis Reynolds Naylor--this is a beautifully done, poignant, funny, serious series of 25 books that begins with Starting with Alice, when Alice McKinley is in about 3rd grade and living in the aftermath of her mother's death. The books mature with Alice.

Janet

